If you are using this tool for research purposes, please cite the following
paper:
L. Schricker, M. Stede, P. Trilcke. Extraction and Classification of Speech, Thought, and Writing in German Narrative Texts. 
In: Proc. of the German Conference on Computational Linguistics (KONVENS). Erlangen, 2019
